title: Good Times Never Felt So Good: Central Adverts, Christmas Day 1994
description:
The next commercial break from the Christmas Day matinee of Mary Poppins starts with an ad for the newly minted Disneyland Paris, in which an adorable small girl with adorable diastema tries to guess the age of her grandfather, Field-Marshal Douglas Haig. The magic of Disney makes him younger I guess. Hopefully they left before he reverted into a foetus.

Next, SURFING GNARLY FROSTIES SURFING SURFING. Another showing for this inappropriately timed breakfast cereal advert with breakers big as condos. Why this is going out on Christmas day is beyond me. Maybe Tony is Jewish.

Then, Lunn Poly again! Whereas the previous one, featuring Father Christmas back-talking to his reindeer, had a fairly short shelf-life for obvious reasons, this one with the snowmen would generally last the entire winter, unto March or so. The lipless puppets make for easier redubbing, too. Note the xylophone adaptation of Walking in the Air on the soundtrack.

Now, I'm sure you were getting worried that there weren't any sales this time around. Don't worry, here's some Raymond Briggsian animation and a song by the Commodores - rerecorded by session artists, naturally - to draw your attention to the January sales at Debenhams. I don't like department stores. They're too big. I drown.

Then, the DFS hivemind returns and Commander Vorshak gets another chance to assert his alpha-male status "Don't-" "DON'T MISS IT AT DFS". You half expect him to piss on her leg for good measure.

Next, a faintly creepy advert for an toothbrush made by Braun in association with Oral-B, which has the feel of some strange cult video communique. "Ask your dentist about plaque removal", it starkly commands you, albeit in friendly sentence-cased sans serifs.

Then suddenly it cuts straight to another advert without any transition whatsoever - which all adverts do these days, of course, ever since some bright spark figured out that if you took all the nanoseconds of dead air in between adverts and put them together, there's space for another advert. It was still unusual in 1994, though, and signified a company buying up twice as much space in a single break as usual. In this case, Braun, who, having dazzled you with a toothbrush, are now explaining why you should buy their razors. The setup is pure screwball comedy, but the tone is...well, a razor advert. Lips Woman and Guy Who Thinks He's Fabulous accidentally swap cases; she manages to figure out who to give it back to by simply zoning in on the smuggest, most self-satisfied douchemule on the train.

Appropriately enough, after that we get some aftershave. At this point Lynx is still concentrating on how great the blokes who use Lynx are, instead of how Lynx will somehow make women spontaneously have sex with you. Which has never happened.

Then, Duke Nukem's daughter runs around in that Magnet advert again. Then, there's a sale on at The Power People in Bicester, Oxford, Swindon, Aylesbury and Mars, with particular focus on the also-ran name in white goods, AEG. They have an eco model, which you know is environmentally friendly because it's intercut with a wave crashing on the shore. AEG died some time in the oughties, although the name is still around today, bought by Electrolux for pennies; their current slogan is "perfekt in form und funktion", which is taking the piss out of something and I'm not sure what.

Finally, Crisco again, promising free headboards with every bed, which strikes me as like promising free legs.

title: DIE SUPERBULLEN Trailer 2 (Ab 6.1.11 im Kino)
description: http://www.facebook.com/superbullen.film.de Nun, zwölf Jahre später, kehren Tommie (Tom Gerhardt) und Mario (Hilmi Sözer) wieder auf die große Kinoleinwand zurück. Die zwei Underdogs aus Köln-Kalk, sind die dümmsten Polizisten Deutschlands und stehen kurz vor ihrer Entlassung. (Auch die Frage drängt: Wie kommen zwei derartige Loser überhaupt zur Polizei?) Doch da naht ihr bislang größter Fall: Der Geißbock „Hennes, geliebtes Kult-Maskottchen des 1. FC Köln, ist entführt worden! Der Verein, die Spieler und natürlich die Fans sind am Boden zerstört. Ohne den Talisman können die Profis den Pokalsieg vergessen. Tommie und Mario, beide glühende FC-Fans, sehen endlich ihre Chance, sich als echte Superbullen zu beweisen und für alle Zeiten unkündbar zu machen Eine hochchaotische Jagd quer durch Deutschland beginnt. Und schon bald glauben die beiden zu wissen, wo sich der Geißbock befindet: Er kann nur in München sein, nirgends anders als beim FC Bayern, dem Gegner im Pokalfinale ... es kommt zum dramatischen Showdown in der Allianz-Arena, wo Tommie und Mario allerdings selbst die größten Böcke schießen...

title: Eten we teveel suiker?
description:
Jaarlijks eten we gemiddeld 45 kilogram suiker. Dat is heel wat. Ook getest op mensen toog naar de gemeentelijke bassischool Sint-Brixius-Rode in Meise. Waarom eten kinderen zo graag suiker? En waarom eten ze er zo veel van? Twee dagen lang hebben we 40 kinderen van het vierde leerjaar op de proef gesteld.
De eerste dag kreeg de helft van de kinderen traditionele, minder zoete ontbijtgranen aangeboden en de andere helft gezoete ontbijtgranen. Wat bleek? De kinderen die gezoete ontbijtgranen kregen, aten maar liefst 30% meer dan de kinderen die traditionele ontbijtgranen kregen. Zoet doet dus eten!

Xuất phát từ sự hối thúc sâu sa của việc hợp tác lâu dài, tin cậy với khách hàng, Hamisa đã và đang cung cấp ra thị trường những sản phẩm dịch vụ có tính năng ưu việt, giá cả cạnh tranh cao và hướng trọng tâm vào từng nhóm khách hàng riêng biệt như:
 
- Tư vấn thương hiệu
- Thiết kế bộ nhận diện thương hiệu
- Marketing trên mạng xã hội (Youtube, Facebook, Forum…)
- Dịch vụ PR cho doanh nghiệp
- Sản suất TVC, Video clip
  …….

Đến nay, Hamisa đã tham gia tư vấn phát triển thương hiệu và thực hiện hoạt động truyền thông tích hợp cho nhiều doanh nghiệp vừa và nhỏ tại Việt Nam như: Tập đoàn dược phẩm Việt Nam, Tập đoàn công nghệ CMC, Trung tâm mua sắm Sài Gòn Nguyễn Kim; Prudential Việt Nam; sữa Physiolac từ Pháp…
Tại Hamisa, định hướng khách hàng là một yêu sách tối cao, mà thông qua đó, chúng tôi có thể đặt mình vào vị trí của khách hàng nhằm chia sẻ đến cùng những khó khăn, thách thức để cùng khách hàng đi tới những thành công lâu dài.

title: Behind the scenes on our TV commercial - Alzheimer's Society
description:
Take a behind the scenes look at how Alzheimer's Society made our TV commercial and hear from the people who created it.

For the first time ever, Alzheimer’s Society is running an advertising campaign to make people more aware of the Society and how we can support people affected by dementia.

Our research shows us that many people still believe that dementia is a normal part of getting old and the main symptom is loss of memory. However, the TV ad featuring a typical family sitting down to a Sunday lunch, shows how isolating it can be for someone with dementia, even as part of a warm and loving family.

Interested in getting the latest updates from the Society?
Follow us on Twitter -- http://www.twitter.com/alzheimerssoc
Like us on Facebook - https://www.facebook.com/alzheimerssocietyuk
___

Who are we?

Alzheimer's Society is the leading support and research charity for people with dementia, their families and carers.
 
What is dementia?

The term 'dementia' is used to describe the symptoms that occur when the brain is affected by specific diseases and conditions. Symptoms of dementia include loss of memory, confusion and problems with speech and understanding.

Support the fight against dementia and visit us at
http://www.alzheimers.org.uk 

If you have concerns about Alzheimer's disease or about any other form of dementia, please contact the Alzheimer's Society National Dementia Helpline on 0300 222 1122.

Alzheimer's Society
Leading the fight against dementia

title: Rube Goldberg style Honda Accord commercial - The Cog
description:
There are no computer graphics or digital tricks in these images.

Everything that you see happened in real time exactly as you see it. 
The recording required 606 takes and in the first 605 takes there always was something, usually of minor importance, that didn't work.
It was necessary for the recording team to install the set-up time after time and it took several months to achieve.

This commercial (at the time) turned out to be the most displayed in the history of the Internet.

There are only six Honda Accords built by hand in the whole world, and to the horror of Honda engineers, the recording team disassembled two of them for the recording.
Everything you see in the sequence (besides the walls, floor, ramp and still mostly assembled Honda Accord) is part of those two automobiles.
The voice is that of Garrison Keiller.

The commercial was so well received by Honda execs when they saw it, that their first comment was how amazing the computer graphics were. They almost fell out of their chairs when told that the recording was real without any graphics manipulation.

By the way, about the wind shield wipers in the new Honda Accords, they were sensitive to water and designed to start working as soon as they get wet. The tires were weighted heavily on the right side, which is how they 'roll uphill'.

Herzlich Willkommen in der bunten Welt von HARIBO, der Heimat der einzigartigen GOLDBÄREN und vieler weiterer köstlich-bunter Süßigkeiten! Bei HARIBO gibt es nicht einfach nur Gummibärchen, sondern GOLDBÄREN. Das ist ein großer Unterschied, denn GOLDBÄREN stehen seit Jahrzehnten für eine einzigartige Kombination aus Freude, Geschmack und Qualität. Welche Gummibärchen könnten diesem Anspruch besser gerecht werden, als das Original HARIBO GOLDBÄREN? 
„HARIBO macht Kinder froh und Erwachsene ebenso" -- für HARIBO ist das nicht nur ein Motto, sondern ein Versprechen, das wir täglich auf´ s Neue mit unserem Fruchtgummi, Lakritz, Weingummi und vieler weiterer Köstlichkeiten einlösen. Ob Schlümpfe oder Kirschen, Süßes oder Saures, fruchtig oder würzig, weich oder fest, mit Salz oder Zucker garniert -- HARIBO bietet eine schier grenzenlose Vielfalt an Formen, Farben und Geschmacksrichtungen. Ananas, Orange, Erdbeere, Apfel, Zitrone, Himbeere, Cola, Melone, Rhabarber und so weiter, und so weiter -- hier ist garantiert für jeden Geschmack etwas dabei. Präsentiert wird die bunte Angebotsvielfalt vom sympathischen HARIBO Goldbären und vom langjährigen HARIBO Werbepartner Thomas Gottschalk. In dieser Kombination ist Spaß und Freude garantiert. Hunderte von unterhaltsamen Werbe- und Doku-Filmen sind in der fast 100-jähirgen Erfolgsgeschichte von HARIBO entstanden. 
Wir laden alle Besucher herzlich ein, hier in die bunte Welt von HARIBO aus fröhlich bewegten Bildern einzutauchen...

title: HEARTS OF THE WEST (Original Theatrical Trailer)
description:
Before garnering multiple award nominations embodying the grit of the Wild West, Jeff Bridges starred in this true gem
of a film, a light hearted look at the classic Hollywood Western and those who made them. Overlooked at the time of its release by an audience put off by its poetic but opaque title, HEARTS OF THE WEST is a jewel ripe for rediscovery. Produced in the wave of '70s "Hollywood historicals", HEARTS OF THE WEST tells the tale of a young writer and Western fan who goes west as a young man and through a combination of crime and happenstance finds himself stepping into a pair of celluloid spurs. Directed by Howard Zieff with Blythe Danner, Andy Griffith and Alan Arkin bringing their "A" game to this B-movie homage (Arkin would win the NY Film Critic's Best Supporting Actor award for his performance).

title: ผู้ชายลัลล้า Lulla Man  [thai trailer 2010]
description:
ผู้ชายลัลล้า Lulla Man สูตร 3G ซ่าส์ ซ่าส์ หากิ๊ก 

นักแสดง : 
ชาคริต แย้มนาม, ส้ม -- ธรรมรส ใจชื่น, นก -- อุษณีย์ วัฒฐานะ, เจี๊ยบ เชิญยิ้ม, เกลือ เป็นต่อ, ฮันนี่ -- ภัสสร, หนูเล็ก ก่อนบ่าย และทีมตลกทั่วฟ้าเมืองไทย 

เรื่องย่อ 
เรื่องราวมันส์ๆ ขำๆ ซึ้งๆ ของสามยอดชายแห่งแก๊ง3G เพื่อนซี้ผู้รักการลัลล้าเป็นชีวิตจิตใจ แม้ภรรยาจะโหดแค่ไหน ก็ยังพลิ้วไหวหนีไปมีกิ๊กได้ตลอด แทน(ชาคริต) จุ้น(เกลือ) ตู๋ (เจี๊ยบ เชิญยิ้ม) ในวีรกรรมสุดแสบซ่าส์กับการหลบหลีกศรีภรรยาสุดโหด! ด้วยฝีมือกะล่อนขั้นเทพ แต่มีรึที่แก๊งภรรยาจะยอมง่ายๆ และแล้วมาตรการขอคืนพื้นที่หัวใจก็เกิดขึ้น เมื่อโบว์ (ส้ม ธรรมรส ) น้อยหน่า(หนูเล็ก ก่อนบ่าย) เจ๊จุ๋ม(ฮันนี่ ภัสสร) ตามจับผิดติดตามพฤติกรรมทุกฝีก้าวชนิดGPSยังเรียกแม่ สามีตัวดียังแอบไปจี๋จ๋าสปาร์ครัก ซูซี่(นก อุษณีย์) นางแบบสุดฮ๊อต โดยหารู้ไม่ว่ากำลังกระตุกหนวดเสือเจ้าพ่ออย่างจัง และสุดท้ายเหมือนว่าสถานการณ์จะดีขึ้นเรื่อยๆ แต่ทว่า...คนมันเคยเจ้าชู้ จะหยุดลัลล้าได้จริงเร้อ...

title: Pawn Stars: Teddy Ruxpin & Grubby
description:
Teddy Ruxpin & Grubby toys appear on this episode of Pawn Stars, "Late Night Chum". I just happened to catch Pawn Stars on July 31, 2012, and luckily caught a rerun of this episode!! Sorry for the poor clarity, but it's my cheap cable.

Believe it or not, a 20-something college kid in 2005 argued with me that the 1980's Teddy Ruxpin wasn't that big, and there was no "yellow thing" back then either. Obviously, he's too young to remember the 1980's, but I'm not, I was 9 when they debuted, and yes, BOTH Teddy Ruxpin AND Grubby debuted in the mid-80's. He thought his early-90's Teddy was an 80's Teddy, obviously taking the stance since he didn't remember, it wasn't true. Kid, if you ever see this, take it from someone who LIVED the 1980's, THEY WERE BOTH AROUND IN 1985!!!

title: Kurdish commercial for the Babylon Festival !
The making of.....Holden Thunder Ute TV commercial
description:
Ever wondered what goes into shooting a Holden TV ad?

We asked the team behind the Holden Thunder Ute TV commercial to give us a look behind the scenes..

The commercial was filmed on location at Avalon Airport, Victoria

3 hours footage was filmed in total -- 2 of the car and 1 of the bull

A team of 40 people took part in the shoot, including actors, film crew, locations team, wardrobe, Holden reps and more.....and we filmed not 1, but 2 angry bulls! 

Then the team spent 6 days in post production, to get the finished ad.

www.holden.com.au/vehicles/ute/thunder

Na,na,na,na,na....

title: [AD STARS 2014/Gold] 'SIGNATURE BOTTLE'
description:
Aershan, a bottled water brand, is famous for its natural mineral water. As the company gets water from nature, they know water scarcity and the importance of water-saving quite well. The client wanted to establish an environmental-friendly image and increase brand awareness.

The unique insight which shaped the idea was that people in large groups when drinking bottled water easily throw half empty bottles away because they forget which bottle is theirs. On the bottle label, we paint a layer of coating that can be easily scratched off. People can just use their finger to mark their bottle however they want, like with their name, a sign or an even artistic picture. Now each water bottle becomes unique and easy to distinguish.

The brand has successfully created an environmentally friendly impression. The campaign also added another element described as “art on the bottle”, winning more favor of consumers and raising brand awareness. Client’s Weibo (Chinese twitter) followers have increased 38% after the launching of the new bottle. The campaign has made more than 230,000 impressions within one month, helping boost sales increase.

‪#‎ADSTARS2014_Gold‬

Brand_Aershan
Agency_Cheil China

title: Samsung TV Commercial~Judd The Head Hunter!
description: Hey Guys, I have not been myself lately so that's why no new videos for awhile.  I want nothing more than to get back into the swing of things and start making new videos.  I miss you guys very much.  Any words of encouragment would be awesome.  Anyways, here is a TV Commercial I did back in September 2011.  As soon as I got back from the island we had filmed this, I went into my Diabetic Shock thingy.  It was weird like something from flying or whatever had pushed my body over the edge and finally the signs of diabetes kicked in.  I am feeling alot better now days.  It's all a mental game now that I am starting to win.  The family is doing awesome and they all miss you as well.  I will be making videos again soon...maybe even today.  I just want to share this with you guys and hope it brings a smile to your face.  God Bless all of you who support me and make me feel special everyday.  Please Rate, Comment and Subscribe to me and my family!
